# Water Glossary

This glossary explains the terms used throughout **Flagstaff Water Futures**. It is written for residents, decision-makers, and technical readers who may not work with water systems every day.

Use the pages in this section to look up:

- water-supply and groundwater terms;
- wastewater and reclaimed-water terms;
- Advanced Water Treatment (AWT) processes;
- Red Gap Ranch (RGR) terminology;
- contaminants and water-quality measurements;
- project funding and regulatory acronyms; and
- common units and conversions.

